# 🛒 E-Commerce Website

## 📌 Project Description
This is a fully functional eCommerce website developed using HTML, CSS, PHP, and MySQL. It allows users to browse products, add them to cart, and place orders.

## 🚀 Features
- User Registration & Login
- Product Listing with Images
- Add to Cart System
- Checkout Functionality
- Admin Panel (Add, Update, Delete Products)
- Database Integration (MySQL)

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- PHP
- MySQL

